title: Shawn Messenger Fine Art Glass Violets Paperweight
description:
Each violet paperweight is made of hand blown glass, inspired by the flowers in artist Shawn Messenger's garden, designed to create an ethereal, painterly visual effect. Purple violets and green leaves stretch from one side of the piece across the top to the other, floating on a layer of glistening turquoise glass. Made in Toldeo Ohio.

  • Dimensions: 3.5 in.
